<bibRefCitation author="BELOKOBYLSKIJ, S. A." box="[772,1044,1704,1725]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" pagination="163 - 298" refId="ref22378" refString="BELOKOBYLSKIJ, S. A. (1998) Tribe Alysiini. In: Key to the Insects of Russian Far East. Vol. IV. Neuropteroidea, Mecoptera, Hymenoptera, Pt. 3: 163 - 298. [In Russian]" type="book chapter" year="1998">BELOKOBYLSKIJ (1998: 210)</bibRefCitation>
